description: Just my type ... a little rough around the edges, an infantry man. A smoker, a drinker and all around party guy, Jayden makes some confessions in this session that are sure to get you over the edge. His ex-wife was a nympho and she loved to stick things in Jayden's ass and he didn't seem to mind. In fact, he gets really horny just talking about it and decides to give us some very sexy ass play on his on. Jayden is a tough guy with a street-smart sense about him that you're gonna love.
title: Jayden, Scene #01
